Assignment 1 Summary
Purpose: Build a sentiment text classifier using a Deep Averaging Network (DAN) in PyTorch for CS 769 (Advanced NLP) at UW-Madison.

What it does
Trains and evaluates a neural network on two sentiment datasets:

SST (Stanford Sentiment Treebank) — multi-class sentiment
CF-IMDB — binary sentiment (IMDb reviews)
The pipeline: load text → build vocabulary → convert words to IDs → pad mini-batches → train DAN model → evaluate accuracy → save predictions.

